The paper discusses the potential risks related to motion sensors built-in wearable devices and demonstrates abuse opportunities leveraged by advanced neural network architectures. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of computer security (cs.CR), machine learning (cs.LG), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), cybernetics (cs.CY), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
